{"tid":1769113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"12.8民陣遊行，我要再見到萬國旗呀！","createTime":"2019-12-04T15:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T07:15:09.000Z","uid":343006,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"8072811c001a9e49c81d6c134ccda1f9189e69f1","tid":1769113,"uid":343006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"大家，仲記得當日9.29全球反極權大遊行，我地浩浩蕩蕩攞住全球各國國旗嘅震撼嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Y1kzhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Y1kzhP.jpg&h=5b5b0da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊星期日，民陣搞嘅國際人權日遊行，我希望可以重現呢種震撼感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喚醒全世界，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特別係歐盟</span></span></strong>，對基本人權嘅關注！<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人，同埋喺新疆嘅維吾爾族人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比中共踐踏緊基本人權<br />\n情況愈嚟愈嚴竣......<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，好感謝國際文宣Twitter手足嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國通過咗香港人權法，搞到口交部、港共政府驚到連環出聲明強烈遣責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且眾議院啱啱都通過咗維吾爾族人權法，再插多一刀喺中共身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，宜家，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">機會嚟喇飛雲！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地希望令到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更加多國家</span></span></span></strong>跟美國頭，擬定人權法，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成為法例！</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本、澳洲、意大利等等已經著手進行中！<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過遠遠唔夠！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我最想見到嘅係歐盟出手呀！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足們應該都知道，歐盟嗰邊關注緊維吾爾族人喺新疆集中營嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n我地好應該connect埋維吾爾族人(事實上我地都處於同一立場) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nshow比歐盟知道，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地香港同樣都等緊你地出手相助！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重創中共</span></span></strong>嘅大好機會，now or never！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔係想錯過咁好機會吧？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嚟緊12.8遊行，萬國旗約定你，維園見！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"014128f73679b3923108b16e9b09c373392f87e6","tid":1769113,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"有無人知一個月前嘅今日係咩日子？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4d255091de133e1268fc6011d93e677da8a6042","tid":1769113,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c53dd24cec65c4d6fcdda35edb727572a95ec5","tid":1769113,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"12月8 維園見"},{"pid":"359ab58accc0684b12ba54adc3746216c92d702c","tid":1769113,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"12月8 維園見"},{"pid":"081edbc7cfb88b16ba8bdd93c837a40bee10794d","tid":1769113,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"12月8 維園見"},{"pid":"a59013866d236c9b651b9b0231889efca03a171a","tid":1769113,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycHWSe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycHWSe1.jpg&h=c8e4eda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFw408n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFw408n.jpg&h=181bcb6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70a5cb7fe2f55cdc71b8bd4b8ec1c4e1cb2a6b17","tid":1769113,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n入去幫無得上Twitter 響新疆受迫害的Uyghurs 多謝美國議員！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig